snippet.title: Card Crawl Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Card Crawl is a solitaire style Dungeon Crawler played with a modified deck of standard cards.
Available on the App Store - https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/card-crawl/id950955524
Download on Google play - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tinytouchtales.cardcrawl

http://www.cardcrawl.com
